{"title":"根的语言","authors":["尚广占","胡晓光"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"根的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚广占摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡晓光配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你清清楚楚地懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这千丝万缕的血肉之缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以说清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是盘根错节　于是缠缠绵绵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的依恋也是土地的依恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而默默的土地是何等的深情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你化为气管化为血管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将土地的爱恋倾诉给"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些盼归的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会认得的　会懂得的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论是跳舞的枝条还是唱歌的叶片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会识得　这根的语言"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}